snippet.title: ONE PIECE World Seeker - Launch Trailer | PS4, X1, PC
snippet.description:
"I'll protect all of you!" Luffy and friends set out on a new adventure to stop the war on Prison Island. Are you ready to face the many challenges that await you?

ONE PIECE World Seeker releases on March 15th. Order your copy today: http://bandainam.co/ONEPIECE

#ONEPIECEWorldSeeker #OPWS #BandaiNamco
